metrics_conclusion: Baba Yetu has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Melodic Complexity and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion: Baba Yetu has sections analyzed in the following keys: D Major,  and E Major.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: A few things didn't sound quite right to me so I analyzed the orchestral score and put that into Hookpad. Unfortunately, it doesn't support modulation and Christopher is modulating from D major to C# minor here, so the last chords are spelled in a weird manner. Fortunately, they still sound the same.
